#### Step 4.3: Entity Search

**File:** `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain/montpellier/app/src/server/entities/entity-search-route.ts`

1. Add suggestion query to `buildWorkspaceSearchSQL` (after the observation query block):
```sql
SELECT id, "suggestion" AS kind, text AS text, search::score(1) AS score
FROM suggestion WHERE text @1@ ${q} AND workspace = $workspace ORDER BY score DESC LIMIT $limit;
```

2. Add suggestion query to `buildProjectSearchSQL`. Since suggestions use `suggests_for` relation (not `belongs_to`), the project-scoped query needs a separate approach:
```sql
LET $suggestion_ids = SELECT VALUE in FROM suggests_for WHERE out = $project;

SELECT id, "suggestion" AS kind, text AS text, search::score(1) AS score
FROM suggestion WHERE text @1@ ${q} AND workspace = $workspace AND id IN $suggestion_ids ORDER BY score DESC LIMIT $limit;
```

Alternatively, for simplicity in the initial implementation, include all workspace suggestions in project search too (since suggestions are not strictly scoped to projects via `belongs_to`). This is the same approach used for observations in the project search currently.

